- Business Type: luxury bridal makeup and styling
- Description: A luxury bridal makeup and styling studio in Delhi specializing in polished, high-touch wedding looks through private consultations and premium in-studio service.
- Target Audience: Brides and families seeking a premium wedding beauty experience
